OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail time and
OL,4,Clarger fines as government tightens
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FWater firm bosses could face up to two
OL,8,Fyears in jail for obstructing
OL,9,Fregulators under new laws proposed
OL,10,Fdesigned at cracking down on the
OL,11,Fpollution of England's rivers, seas
OL,12,Fand lakes.
OL,14,FThe Water (Special Measures) Bill,
OL,15,Fintroduced to Parliament on Wednesday,
OL,16,Fwill hand new powers to Ofwat and the
OL,17,FEnvironment Agency to take action on
OL,18,Fcompanies damaging the environment and
OL,19,Ffailing customers.
