OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FThe government said the current
OL,8,Fenforcement system is insufficient to
OL,9,Fhold firms accountable for widespread
OL,10,Fillegality in the sector, citing that
OL,11,Fonly three individuals have been
OL,12,Fcriminally prosecuted by the
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency without appeal
OL,14,Fsince privatisation.
