OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail time and
OL,4,Clarger fines as government tightens
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FUnder the bill, harsher penalties for
OL,8,Flaw-breaking will be introduced,
OL,9,Fincluding jail sentences of up to two
OL,10,Fyears for executives who fail to
OL,11,Fcooperate or obstruct Environment
OL,12,FAgency and Drinking Water Inspectorate
OL,13,Finvestigations.
OL,15,FThe burden of proof in civil cases
OL,16,Fwill be lowered so that the
OL,17,FEnvironment Agency can bring forward
OL,18,Fcriminal charges against bosses more
OL,19,Feasily.
