OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail time and
OL,4,Clarger fines as government tightens
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FRegulators will also be empowered to
OL,8,Fban bonus payments to water bosses if
OL,9,Fthey fail to meet high standards to
OL,10,Fprotect the environment, their
OL,11,Fconsumers and their company's finances.
OL,13,FYears of under-investment by privately
OL,14,Frun firms combined with ageing water
OL,15,Finfrastructure, a growing population
OL,16,Fand more extreme weather caused by
OL,17,Fclimate change have seen the quality
OL,18,Fof England's rivers, lakes and oceans
OL,19,Fplummet in recent years.
