OL,7,FSewage spills have contributed to a
OL,8,Fsituation in which no single river in
OL,9,FEngland is considered to be in good
OL,10,Foverall health, and beauty spots
OL,11,Fincluding Windermere in the Lake
OL,12,FDistrict have been polluted.
OL,14,FSome water utilities are also creaking
OL,15,Funder high levels of debt or face
OL,16,Fcriticism over dividends to
OL,17,Fshareholders and executive bonuses.
