OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail time and
OL,4,Clarger fines as government tightens
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FIt comes as part of plans for a
OL,8,Fbroader reset of the sector over this
OL,9,Fparliament, including legislation to
OL,10,Fspeed up sewage infrastructure
OL,11,Fupgrades and to address how the water
OL,12,Findustry is run so that it can still
OL,13,Fattract investment and talent,
OL,14,Fofficials indicated.
OL,16,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,17,F"The public are furious that in 21st
OL,18,Fcentury Britain, record levels of
OL,19,Fsewage are being pumped into our
OL,20,Frivers, lakes and seas.
