OL,5,Crules
OL,7,F"Under this government, water
OL,8,Fexecutives will no longer line their
OL,9,Fown pockets whilst pumping out this
OL,10,Ffilth. If they refuse to comply, they
OL,11,Fcould end up in the dock and face
OL,12,Fprison time."
OL,14,FUnder the proposed laws, regulators
OL,15,Fwill be able to issue severe and
OL,16,Fautomatic fines without having to
OL,17,Fdirect resources to lengthy
OL,18,Finvestigations, the government said.
