OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FThe legislation will also require
OL,8,Findependent monitoring of every sewage
OL,9,Foutlet and the reporting of discharges
OL,10,Fwithin the hour of the initial spill.
OL,12,FCurrently, some 14,000 storm overflows
OL,13,Facross England are monitored so that
OL,14,Fany discharge of untreated sewage
OL,15,Fduring periods of heavy rain can be
OL,16,Freported.
