OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail time and
OL,4,Clarger fines as government tightens
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FHowever, water firms will now be
OL,8,Frequired to fully monitor the 7,000
OL,9,Femergency overflows, which are only
OL,10,Fpermitted to discharge raw sewage as a
OL,11,Flast resort from the network in the
OL,12,Fevent of issues such as power outages
OL,13,For pump failures.
OL,15,FThe firms will then be required to
OL,16,Fpublish real-time data for all
OL,17,Femergency overflows to ensure
OL,18,Ftransparency and alert the public.
