OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail time and
OL,4,Clarger fines as government tightens
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FTo ensure regulators are properly
OL,8,Ffunded, the bill will expand powers
OL,9,Ffor the watchdogs to recover costs
OL,10,Ffrom water companies for enforcement
OL,11,Faction taken in response to their
OL,12,Ffailings.
OL,14,FOfwat will also be required to set
OL,15,Frules that ensure companies appoint
OL,16,Fdirectors and chief executives, and
OL,17,Fallow them to remain in post, only
OL,18,Fwhen they meet the highest standards
OL,19,Fof "fitness and propriety".
